base64url.title: Base64url
base64url.description: Binary data encoded as a url-safe string as defined in [RFC4648](https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc4648#section-5)

byte.title: Byte
byte.description: base64 encoded data as defined in [RFC4648](https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc4648#section-4)

date-time.title: Date Time
date-time.description: date and time as defined by date-time - [RFC3339](https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc3339#section-5.6)

decimal.title: Decimal
decimal.description: A fixed point decimal number of unspecified precision and range

decimal128.title: Decimal128
decimal128.description: A decimal floating-point number with 34 significant decimal digits

double-int.title: Double Int
double-int.description: an integer that can be stored in an IEEE 754 double-precision number without loss of precision

duration.title: Duration
duration.description: duration as defined by duration - RFC3339

email.title: Email
email.description: An email address as defined as Mailbox in RFC5321

hostname.title: Hostname
hostname.description: A host name as defined by RFC1123

http-date.title: Http Date
http-date.description: date and time as defined by HTTP-date - [RFC7231](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc7231#section-7.1.1.1)

idn-email.title: Idn Email
idn-email.description: An email address as defined as Mailbox in RFC6531

idn-hostname.title: Idn Hostname
idn-hostname.description: An internationalized host name as defined by RFC5890

ipv4.title: Ipv4
ipv4.description: An IPv4 address as defined as dotted-quad by RFC2673

ipv6.title: Ipv6
ipv6.description: An IPv6 address as defined by RFC4673

iri-reference.title: Iri Reference
iri-reference.description: A Internationalized Resource Identifier as defined in RFC3987

iri.title: Iri
iri.description: A Internationalized Resource Identifier as defined in RFC3987

json-pointer.title: Json Pointer
json-pointer.description: A JSON string representation of a JSON Pointer as defined in RFC6901

media-range.title: Media Range
media-range.description: A media type as defined by the `media-range` ABNF production in RFC9110.

password.title: Password
password.description: a string that hints to obscure the value.

regex.title: Regex
regex.description: A regular expression as defined in ECMA-262

relative-json-pointer.title: Relative Json Pointer
relative-json-pointer.description: A JSON string representation of a relative JSON Pointer as defined in draft RFC 01

sf-binary.title: Sf Binary
sf-binary.description: structured fields byte sequence as defined in [RFC8941]

sf-boolean.title: Sf Boolean
sf-boolean.description: structured fields boolean as defined in [RFC8941]

sf-decimal.title: Sf Decimal
sf-decimal.description: structured fields decimal as defined in [RFC8941]

sf-integer.title: Sf Integer
sf-integer.description: structured fields integer as defined in [RFC8941]

sf-string.title: Sf String
sf-string.description: structured fields string as defined in [RFC8941]

sf-token.title: Sf Token
sf-token.description: structured fields token as defined in [RFC8941]

time.title: Time
time.description: time as defined by full-time - RFC3339

uri-reference.title: Uri Reference
uri-reference.description: A URI reference as defined in [RFC3986](https://www.rfc-editor.org/info/rfc3986)

uri-template.title: Uri Template
uri-template.description: A URI Template as defined in RFC6570

uri.title: Uri
uri.description: A Uniform Resource Identifier as defined in RFC3986

uuid.title: Uuid
uuid.description: A Universally Unique IDentifier as defined in RFC4122
